- Add app/components/PosterCard.tsx: extracted card component
- Update auth.ts and all API routes to use getDb()
- Remove all debug markers, routeMarker, timings from routes
- Rename proxy.ts -> middleware.ts, fix export name (was silently dead)
- Slim page.tsx: 168 -> 55 lines
- Slim selected/page.tsx: 176 -> 65 lines
- Delete dead files: PDFviewer.tsx, starred/page.tsx, posters/upload/route.ts, redeploy.txt
